  1→//axhob_operation
  2→{rbtgo_director_create}
  3→
  4→The
  5→{rbtr_governor}
  6→creates a
  7→{rbtr_director}
  8→{giam_service_account}
  9→with build management permissions:
 10→
 11→//axhoq_precondition
 12→* Execute {rbtoe_check_rubric_repo_url} (validates {rbrr_rubric_repo_url} using PAT from Secret Manager)
 13→
 14→//axhoq_precondition
 15→* Execute {rbtoe_check_cbv2_connection} to verify {rbtgi_cbv2_connection} is active
 16→
 17→//axhop_parameter_from_type
 18→{rbtr_director}
 19→. *Validate Input Parameters*:
 20→.. {rbbc_require}
 21→`«INPUT_INSTANCE»` provided as first argument
 22→.. {rbbc_store}
 23→`«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»` as `rb-director-«INPUT_INSTANCE»`
 24→.. {rbbc_store}
 25→`«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` as `«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»@{rbrr_depot_project_id}.iam.gserviceaccount.com`
 26→
 27→//axhoq_precondition
 28→* {rbbc_require}
 29→`BURD_OUTPUT_DIR` environment variable set and directory exists
 30→
 31→//axhos_step
 32→. *Authenticate as
 33→{rbtr_governor}*:
 34→.. Execute
 35→{rbtoe_governor_authenticate}
 36→.. {rbbc_store}
 37→`«GOVERNOR_TOKEN»` for subsequent API calls
 38→
 39→//axhos_step
 40→. *Create
 41→{rbtr_director}
 42→Service Account*:
 43→.. {rbbc_call}
 44→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/create[iam.serviceAccounts.create] with:
 45→... accountId: `«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»`
 46→... displayName: `Recipe Bottle Director («INPUT_INSTANCE»)`
 47→... description: `Create/destroy container images for «INPUT_INSTANCE»`
 48→... project:
 49→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 50→.. {rbbc_require}
 51→HTTP 200 response
 52→.. {rbbc_store}
 53→`«DIRECTOR_UNIQUE_ID»` from response `.uniqueId` field
 54→
 55→//axhos_step
 56→. *Verify Service Account Propagation*:
 57→.. {rbbc_call}
 58→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/get[iam.serviceAccounts.get] for `projects/-/serviceAccounts/«DIRECTOR_UNIQUE_ID»`
 59→.. {rbbc_poll}
 60→with backoff until HTTP 200 (newly-created SA may not be immediately resolvable by numeric ID)
 61→.. NOTE: Numeric ID is valid in API URL paths but subject to IAM propagation delay. Not valid in IAM policy `members` — see RBS0 IAM Member Format.
 62→.. {rbbc_require}
 63→service account accessible
 64→
 65→//axhos_step
 66→. *Preflight: Ensure Pristine Key State*:
 67→.. {rbbc_call}
 68→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts.keys/list[serviceAccounts.keys.list] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»`
 69→.. {rbbc_store}
 70→`«EXISTING_KEYS»` from response `.keys[]`
 71→.. {rbbc_require}
 72→no keys with `keyType: USER_MANAGED` exist
 73→.. {rbbc_fatal}
 74→if USER_MANAGED keys found: "Manual cleanup required via Console"
 75→
 76→//axhos_step
 77→. *Generate Service Account Key*:
 78→.. {rbbc_call}
 79→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts.keys/create[serviceAccounts.keys.create] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with:
 80→... privateKeyType: `TYPE_GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS_FILE`
 81→.. {rbbc_store}
 82→`«DIRECTOR_PRIVATE_KEY_DATA»` from response `.privateKeyData` field
 83→.. {rbtoe_rbra_generate}
 84→converts `«DIRECTOR_PRIVATE_KEY_DATA»` to `«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»`
 85→
 86→//axhos_step
 87→. *Get Depot Project Number*:
 88→.. {rbbc_call}
 89→link:https://cloud.google.com/resource-manager/reference/rest/v3/projects/get[projects.get] for
 90→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 91→.. {rbbc_store}
 92→`«PROJECT_NUMBER»` from `.projectNumber` field
 93→
 94→//axhos_step
 95→. *Grant Project-Level Permissions*:
 96→.. {rbbc_call}
 97→link:https://cloud.google.com/resource-manager/reference/rest/v3/projects/setIamPolicy[projects.setIamPolicy] for
 98→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 99→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with roles:
100→... `roles/cloudbuild.builds.editor` (submit and manage builds)
101→... `roles/viewer` (read project resources)
102→... `roles/cloudbuild.connectionAdmin` (CB v2 connection and repository management)
103→.. Policy version: 3
104→.. {rbbc_require}
105→IAM policy update successful
106→
107→//axhos_step
108→. *Grant Secret Manager Access for Inscribe*:
109→.. NOTE:
110→{rbtr_director}
111→needs to fetch the GitLab project access token from Secret Manager during
112→{rbtgo_rubric_inscribe}
113→to construct authenticated git URLs.
114→.. {rbbc_call}
115→link:https://cloud.google.com/secret-manager/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.secrets/getIamPolicy[secrets.getIamPolicy] for `projects/{rbrr_depot_project_id}/secrets/RBGC_CBV2_API_TOKEN_SECRET_NAME`
116→.. {rbbc_require}
117→HTTP 200 — existing policy must be read successfully before modification. Die on failure; a silent fallback to empty policy would destroy existing bindings (e.g., the Cloud Build service agent binding set by {rbtgo_depot_create}).
118→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` to `roles/secretmanager.secretAccessor` in the existing policy (read-modify-write)
119→.. {rbbc_call}
120→link:https://cloud.google.com/secret-manager/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.secrets/setIamPolicy[secrets.setIamPolicy] with the updated policy
121→.. {rbbc_require}
122→IAM binding successful — existing bindings preserved
123→
124→//axhos_step
125→. *Grant
126→{rbtr_mason}
127→Impersonation*:
128→.. NOTE:
129→{rbtr_director}
130→submits builds that execute as
131→{rbtr_mason}.
132→This requires `serviceAccountUser` permission on
133→{rbtr_mason}.
134→.. {rbbc_call}
135→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/setIamPolicy[serviceAccounts.setIamPolicy] for
136→{rbtr_mason}
137→service account
138→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with `roles/iam.serviceAccountUser`
139→.. {rbbc_require}
140→IAM binding successful
141→
142→//axhos_step
143→. *Grant
144→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
145→Access*:
146→.. {rbbc_call}
147→link:https://cloud.google.com/storage/docs/json_api/v1/buckets/setIamPolicy[buckets.setIamPolicy] for
148→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
149→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with roles:
150→... `roles/storage.objectCreator` (upload sources)
151→... `roles/storage.objectViewer` (verify uploads)
152→.. {rbbc_require}
153→bucket IAM update successful
154→
155→//axhos_step
156→. *Grant
157→{rbtgi_repository}
158→Admin Access*:
159→.. {rbbc_call}
160→link:https://cloud.google.com/artifact-registry/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.locations.repositories/setIamPolicy[repositories.setIamPolicy] for
161→{rbtgi_repository}
162→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with `roles/artifactregistry.repoAdmin`
163→.. {rbbc_require}
164→repository IAM update successful
165→
166→//axhoo_output_of_type
167→{rbtgi_rbra_file}
168→. *Display Installation Instructions*:
169→.. {rbbc_show}
170→Director created successfully
171→.. {rbbc_show}
172→RBRA file location: `«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»`
173→.. {rbbc_show}
174→installation command:
175→... `cp "«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»" "{rbrr_director_rbra_file}"`
176→.. {rbbc_warn}
177→if
178→{rbrr_director_rbra_file}
179→already exists
180→
181→//axhoc_completion
182→Successful execution creates director service account.
183→
